{"tid":1805222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣人民共產黨疑涉賄招待遊江西 南檢傳喚60多人","createTime":"2019-12-31T13:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T19:41:22.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2147d1e1e472f6920b31caf31460efa5426f0d","tid":1805222,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"台灣人民共產黨疑涉賄招待遊江西 南檢傳喚60多人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3025280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3025280&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=f040444f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3025280&h=312b1d74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3025280</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕檢調獲報，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「台灣人民共產黨」發起人林德旺涉嫌招待70多人到中國江西遊玩，途中疑似呼籲支持台南某立委候選人，以及政黨票投特定統派，台南地檢署昨天傳喚60多人到案，全案依違反國安法、選罷法擴大偵辦中。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《聯合報》 報導，林德旺疑似在本月5日至12日，招待成員到江西旅遊，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過程中發放台灣人民共產黨背心，並宣傳台南第1選區某立委候選人、政黨票投特定統派，過程中還接受國台辦官員招待</span></strong>，參加者包括合併前的新營市長黃金鏞、台灣人民共產黨副總理郭文東、呂欣尚。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，郭文東強調沒人認識該立委候選人，且自費14500元團費參訪古蹟，過程都沒談過選舉。林德旺5天前抵達，尚未返台，將待他回國後要求到案說明案情。"},{"pid":"1722b2175f910f0523aef4f950b95e7c46023d8d","tid":1805222,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:31:44.000Z","msg":"即刻做野"},{"pid":"919174fe613114ad559a8b5b5179c4d2fdc7be5d","tid":1805222,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"清算開始"},{"pid":"432599701455819ca462b4c0bbcd5ad229215996","tid":1805222,"uid":4151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"88c339067dadd8362486742e9fe00fac7db39f4f","tid":1805222,"uid":24345,"like":2,